+/*
+ * Fixed-lobby signaling server for the Ping Pong Go / table-tennis WebRTC game.
+ *
+ * Important compatibility goals:
+ * - Keep the existing hello -> welcome peer-id behavior.
+ * - Keep existing joined/connect/description/candidate/event message names.
+ * - Keep URLs and QR invites as index.html?id=XXX.
+ * - Remove random lobby-code generation completely.
+ *
+ * Debug:
+ *   SIGNAL_DEBUG=1 node signaling-server.js
+ *
+ * Config path:
+ *   LOBBY_CONFIG=/path/to/lobby-config.json node signaling-server.js
+ */
